62.2	Confirmation	Confirmation	Confirmation is a rite of initiation in Christian churches, normally carried out through anointing and/or the laying on of hands and prayer for the purpose of bestowing the Gift of the Holy Spirit.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ea/Confirmation_VanderWeyden.png/220px-Confirmation_VanderWeyden.png
